Larger font size Posted: Sunday, October 18, 2015 2:00 am GIRLS GOLF: Perry’s Allen places eighth among individual qualifers at D-4 state meet The Argus-Press The Argus-Press | 0 comments 
EAST LANSING – Perry’s Kelsi Allen finished eighth among individual qualfiers at Saturday’s MHSAA Division 4 Girls Golf Finals at Forest Akers East. 
Allen shot a 93 round Saturday after shooting 97 during her first round on Friday.
